{"tid":1564274,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唱歌人鏈係支線！五大訴求係主線！揸住核彈去打仗！","createTime":"2019-09-12T16:44:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T00:38:28.000Z","uid":13586,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7287a027b36de7c04edf466c0b00d977050cd7ea","tid":1564274,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:44:55.000Z","msg":"其實而家就好似玩Pokémon 咁：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">打支線：</span></strong><br />\n當然可以做，打npc 升寵加錢學招，送道具送裝備<br />\n<br />\n同樣，加唱歌，人鏈，士氣up團結up，地區性文宣一流<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>但推進劇情記得打主線：</strong></span><br />\n俾你升鯉魚王升到99lv，或者手上有六隻耿鬼都唔去打道館打五大天王一樣冇意思，爆唔到機<br />\n<br />\n同樣，記得星期六日主線任，先可以推進劇情<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fbive60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFbive60.jpg&h=ce2e8cb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知，大家都有工作上家庭上嘅包袱。人會攰，有惰性，我都會，自己發夢發咗幾個月都攰，人好灰，沒完沒了咁，真心諗過退場，甚至quit game<br />\n<br />\n但當鳩叫完唱埋歌，士氣大buff，嗌到把聲都沙埋，所以唔好話支線冇用，打支線就係support你去打主線<br />\n<br />\n仲記唔記得手上得比卡超，你係點打小剛嘅大岩蛇？捉綠毛蟲進化成巴他蝶再打？定狂升肥起？都係為大家support打主線<br />\n<br />\n但唔好做失敗主義，切記：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>兄弟爬山，各自修行<br />\n不分和與勇，核爆都唔割</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n而且我地而家有齊神獸六隻耿鬼<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">同樣我地有核彈：元朗721，太子831，新屋嶺<br />\n仲有導彈：太古掃射，葵芳TG，福建幫，爆頭，盲眼，仲有更多更多</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n仲要攞正牌有外國勢力buff ，猶如99粒復活藥咁打五大天王<br />\n<br />\n呢場仗一定會影響未來五十年，甚至一百年後嘅香港，最後光復香港定中共統治就係睇今次<br />\n<br />\n所以有咩<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">行動post同文宣post一定要推，幫手叫人打主線</span></span></strong>，就算final boss係中共都要打都要贏！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求    缺一不可<br />\n光復香港    時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"bf6d7f36f2429d55eb8f76a51f9b0686c8568714","tid":1564274,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:45:13.000Z","msg":"1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700e698b7b4099129d117907fdd07c2d274b7f96","tid":1564274,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:45:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"8a0e9308da320ca3e88a54f88df0fcad6e68923b","tid":1564274,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:45:25.000Z","msg":"2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a22f7521d6c5a4a8782aaa8e6b259ca88c7c9e07","tid":1564274,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:45:44.000Z","msg":"3/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce98be02e274a9ce4de62b6f949203c7dc8e637a","tid":1564274,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:45:58.000Z","msg":"4/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3178fcf9b5d167b829821ededc660e79bf8bb289","tid":1564274,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:46:11.000Z","msg":"5/1」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135d0061a9d32532ba574816246c6744076bd136","tid":1564274,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"